                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Far enough. Voluntary verification checkpoint. My colleague at the desk handles the paperwork; I handle the part where you do not stroll past without it."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Pay the man his processing fee, turn back, or settle it with me. Company business, all three."
                        }
                    ],
